metadata.title: How Alibaba overcame Beijing's crackdown to become an AI giant
metadata.description: The Alibaba empire was once under intense scrutiny from Beijing and competition from rivals. Now a big AI bet is helping it stage a revival.
metadata.author: Arjun Kharpal
